{"tid":1312344,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論]有冇法律撚可以解釋下公民拘捕權（101A)既疑犯對象可唔可以係警察？","createTime":"2019-07-13T13:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T13:21:25.000Z","uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"183a4d600f318acafc461d7315bc789bcfb11817","tid":1312344,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:21:25.000Z","msg":"近排屎拂痕走去睇左有關行使公民拘捕權既條件同範圍：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201411/26/P201411260502.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201411%2F26%2FP201411260502.htm&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRKzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=150f4d7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201411/26/P201411260502.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n知道咗市民可以進行合理及相稱既武力控制疑犯。假如依家知道疑犯會干犯侵害人身罪條例（212）既話，而犯罪者有機會係警察既時候，市民有冇權去行使拘捕權去拘捕警察？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：法律盲"}]}